bio: Mark Baker
    Mark Baker is the author of _Every Page is Page One: Topic-based Writing for Technical Communication and the Web_ as well as other books on content and content technologies and dozens of articles on technical communication, content strategy, and structured writing. He has worked as a technical writer, tech comm manager, director of communications, trainer, programmer, copywriter, and consultant and has spoken frequently at industry conferences. He had designed, built, and used multiple structured writing tools and systems, including the one used to write this book. He blogs at everypageispageone.com and tweets as @mbakeranalecta. For more information, see analecta.com. 